node.text:
No other financial planner is putting out information like this.

Go drop @ronocaruthers a follow 🔥

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by All About Making Money 💸 on September 15, 2021 tagging @ronocaruthers. May be an image of text that says 'Ron Caruthers @roncaruthers Just helped a young military man set up a tax free retirement plan. He's 26. $600 a month. If he never increases the monthly amount, at age 65 he'll have $1,259,207. And, tax-free income of....wait for it... $99,500 a year. For LIFE.'.

Photo shared by All About Making Money 💸 on September 15, 2021 tagging @ronocaruthers. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'Ron Caruthers @roncaruthers When he retires from the military at 38, he'll also get about $2,500 a month, and go into corporate or government service. Somewhere in there, we'll probably add another one of these accounts, get him investing up to the match in his 401k, and invest in some real estate.'.

Photo shared by All About Making Money 💸 on September 15, 2021 tagging @ronocaruthers. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'Ron Caruthers @roncaruthers I've seen a lot of notes about inflation. Some intelligent, some less so. But, it's a fair point: What WILL $99,500 a year be worth in 39 years? First off, it's tax-free, so whatever rate taxes are at, it's worth that much more.'.

Photo shared by All About Making Money 💸 on September 15, 2021 tagging @ronocaruthers. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'Ron Caruthers @roncaruthers Right now, between that and his military pension, he would be in the 22% bracket. And 6% for the state of CA So, on that money, if it WASN'T tax free, he would have to make $138,194 just to net the $99,500 However, at 3% inflation THAT amount is really only worth about $43,635'.

Photo shared by All About Making Money 💸 on September 15, 2021 tagging @ronocaruthers. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'Ron Caruthers @roncaruthers But, the advantage that THIS account has is that he has access to the money before he's 59 1/2. So, he can use the money for: -a house down payment; -a wedding; -Investments; -Even his own kids's education. His other accounts will force him to pay tax and penalties.'.

Photo shared by All About Making Money 💸 on September 15, 2021 tagging @ronocaruthers. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'Ron Caruthers @roncaruthers So, it's a fair point. On the other hand... 1.1 1. DELIBERATELY used a much more conservative interest rate than what that plan has historically earned so the real numbers are likely to be (somewhat) higher. 2. It's just ONE piece of his financial plan.'.

Photo shared by All About Making Money 💸 on September 15, 2021 tagging @ronocaruthers. May be an image of text that says 'Ron Caruthers @roncaruthers 3. We're also assuming that he never increases his $600/month contributions.....but his salary and income WILL increase over the next 39 years. So, his contributions to this and other accounts will likely increase as well, but I didn't show that.'.

Photo shared by All About Making Money 💸 on September 15, 2021 tagging @ronocaruthers. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'Ron Caruthers @roncaruthers 4. However, for those of you saying that putting $273,600 into an account and getting an income stream of $99,500 a year for the rest of his life is BAD??! He puts in that amount, If he lives to 86, he pulls out $2,189,000 tax free. And still has $1,079,000 in cash.'.

Photo shared by All About Making Money 💸 on September 15, 2021 tagging @ronocaruthers. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'Ron Caruthers @roncaruthers 5. And for those of you that are saying: 'WeLl, hE SHoULd Day TraDe AnD mAkE MOrE' Or put it all in stocks. Maybe he will later. Nothing wrong with that either. But saying he's 'guaranteed' to make a 22% return so he shouldn't do this? Yeah. No.'.

Photo shared by All About Making Money 💸 on September 15, 2021 tagging @ronocaruthers. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'Ron Caruthers @roncaruthers A couple more notes on this I used a properly structured ndex Universal Life Insurance. Key words: Properly structured. So it literally has the least amount of death benefit possible. We're also contributing to a Roth IRA and he has a TSP.'.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by All About Making Money 💸 on September 15, 2021 tagging @bastiaanslot_. May be an image of text that says 'Bastiaan Slot @_bastiaanslot 7 principles that made me a millionaire in my early 20s. (A thread)'.

Photo shared by All About Making Money 💸 on September 15, 2021 tagging @bastiaanslot_. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'Bastiaan Slot @_bastiaanslot Goal setting. If you don't know what you want, then you don't know what to do. Set one clear, tangible goal. Achieve your goal, then repeat.'.

Photo shared by All About Making Money 💸 on September 15, 2021 tagging @bastiaanslot_. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'Bastiaan Slot @_bastiaanslot 2. Sacrifice. If you don't sacrifice for what you want, then your goal becomes the sacrifice.'.

Photo shared by All About Making Money 💸 on September 15, 2021 tagging @bastiaanslot_. May be an image of text that says 'Bastiaan Slot @_bastiaanslot 3. Health. Sleep wel Eat healthy. Meditate. Exercise. Take time to relax. If you aren't performing at your best, your business won't either.'.

Photo shared by All About Making Money 💸 on September 15, 2021 tagging @bastiaanslot_. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'Bastiaan Slot @_bastiaanslot 4. Gratitude. Always looking to the future future can cause fear, anxiety, and stress. Practice gratitude daily to balance yourself.'.

Photo shared by All About Making Money 💸 on September 15, 2021 tagging @bastiaanslot_. May be an image of text that says 'Bastiaan Slot @_bastiaanslot 5. Resist impulses. When you're working, resist all urges to eat snacks, grab a treat, or check social media. Train yourself to stay focused on the task at hand, and don't let anything distract you that's how you make progress.'.

Photo shared by All About Making Money 💸 on September 15, 2021 tagging @bastiaanslot_. May be an image of text that says 'Bastiaan Slot @_bastiaanslot 6. Consistency. Whether you're seeing great results or no results at all, you need to stay consistent. Stay consistent without expecting immediate results. It will all add up long term.'.

Photo shared by All About Making Money 💸 on September 15, 2021 tagging @bastiaanslot_. May be an image of text that says 'Bastiaan Slot @_bastiaanslot 7. Invest in yourself. etc. Whether it's books, mentors, seminars, Make sure you're constantly investing in your own growth. You don't have to figure out everything on your own. Find someone who has the results you want and learn from them. That's your "shortcut" to success.'.

Photo shared by All About Making Money 💸 on September 15, 2021 tagging @bastiaanslot_. May be an image of one or more people and text that says 'Bastiaan Slot @_bastiaanslot Whenever you're feeling stuck or like you're not making progress in life you can always go back to these principles and see where you're goino wrong. |focus on these daily to make sure I stay on track.'.

Photo shared by All About Making Money 💸 on September 15, 2021 tagging @bastiaanslot_. May be an image of text that says 'Bastiaan Slot @_bastiaanslot If you'd like to see more content and tips abon what learned from building a 7-figure consulting business, drop me a follow.'.
